it “[evaluates] different marketing promotions for new members in the future”. The company then rolled out a system where <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/xbox-pc-game-pass-free-trials-3438327">current users could invite five of their friends to free two-week trials</a> of Xbox Game Pass. </p><figure id="attachment_3484493" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3484493" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3484493" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-preloading-starts-this-week.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-preloading-starts-this-week.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-preloading-starts-this-week-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-preloading-starts-this-week-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-preloading-starts-this-week-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-preloading-starts-this-week-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/starfield-preloading-starts-this-week-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3484493" class="wp-caption-text"> &#39;Starfield&#39; Credit: Xbox Game Studios</figcaption></figure><p> Following that, the offer was resurrected in July, but it was shortened to 14 days of Xbox Game Pass for £1 for new customers just a month later.</p><p> Xbox Game Pass is available in three different versions – console, <a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/pc">PC</a> and Ultimate. Ultimate includes both console and PC as well as Xbox Live Gold, which unlocks online console multiplayer modes and a scattering of exclusive <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/electronic-arts">Electronic Arts</a> titles in EA Play.</p><p> As automatic monthly subscriptions, these are priced at £8.99 for console, £7.99 for PC, and £12.99 for Ultimate.</p><p> <em>Starfield</em> launches on September 6 for PC and <a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/xbox-series-xs">Xbox Series X|S</a> , yet those who have purchased the Premium or Constellation editions will be able to access the game five days earlier. </p><figure id="attachment_3249144" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3249144" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3249144" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Starfield-New-Atlantis-2000x1270-1.jpg" alt="星空。 Credit: Bethesda." width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Starfield-New-Atlantis-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Starfield-New-Atlantis-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Starfield-New-Atlantis-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Starfield-New-Atlantis-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Starfield-New-Atlantis-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Starfield-New-Atlantis-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3249144" class="wp-caption-text">星空。 Credit: Bethesda.</figcaption></figure><p> The sci-fi role-playing game is playable through Xbox Game Pass and if players would like to upgrade to the Premium edition for early access and bonus add-ons, like the game&#39;s first expansion, that will cost them £34.99.</p><p> In other news, <em>Starfield</em> director Todd Howard said that <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/bethesdas-todd-howard-says-talking-about-retirement-is-weird-3488033">it would be “weird” to talk about retirement</a> , but he has considered the possibility.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.